metadata.name: BEFORE THE STORIES
metadata.description:
Hi El,
Maybe you have grown up now and do a new journey in your life.
I just want to tell you some story, story about me.
How I grow in this crazy world, how I live with imagination, and how I do believe with what Iâ€™m doing.

In this story, I don't want to patronize you.
But, I just want you to know who am I with the drawings that I've made for you.

Ok, I will start telling you the story.

 -Dad
